    <div class="clear-block clear">&nbsp;</div>
  
  <div class="content"><p>After a decade long rally, gold recroded its biggest two-day drop in 30 years during April. What caused this sudden decline? Is the gold cycle over, or <a href="http://www.zerohedge.com/news/2013-05-10/did-they-ever-tell-you-buy-gold-or-sell-stocks">is this just a dip in the market?</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://uk.saxomarkets.com/fx-debates/gold-rout-infographic"><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/images/user3303/imageroot/2013/05/gold-rout-infographic.jpg" width="583" height="3000" /></a></p>


</div>
