<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3571308">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Thu, 05/16/2013 - 21:04 | <a href="/news/2013-05-16/visualizing-great-gold-rout#comment-3571308" class="active">3571308</a></span>
