<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3571845">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Fri, 05/17/2013 - 00:17 | <a href="/news/2013-05-16/visualizing-great-gold-rout#comment-3571845" class="active">3571845</a></span>
